    <script>
    $(document).ready(
        function() {
            var connectionOptions = {
                "force new connection": true,
                "reconnectionAttempts": "Infinity",
                "timeout": 1000,
                "transports": ["websocket"]
            }

            var socket1 = io.connect('https://nms.lexxadata.net.id:3000/', connectionOptions)
            socket1.on('log_non_physic_ticket', function(msg2) {

                ! function(p) {
                    "use strict";

                    function t() {}
                    t.prototype.send = function(t, i, o, e, n, a, s, r) {
                        var c = {
                            heading: t,
                            text: i,
                            position: o,
                            loaderBg: e,
                            icon: n,
                            hideAfter: 5000,
                            stack: s = s || 1
                        };
                        r && (c.showHideTransition = r), p.toast().reset("all"), p.toast(c)
                    }, p.NotificationApp = new t, p.NotificationApp.Constructor = t
                }(window.jQuery),
                function(i) {
                    "use strict";
                    if (msg2.nama_server == "Lexxa Net") {
                        if (msg2.status == 'FORWARD TO NOC') {
                            i.NotificationApp.send("Forward Ticket " + msg2.ticket_reference + "",
                                "Name : " + msg2.nama + "</p>Priority : " + msg2.priority +
                                "</p>Cause : " + msg2.deskripsi + "</p>By CS: " + msg2.nama_exekutor +
                                "</p>", "top-right", "#bf441d", "error")
                        } else if (msg2.status == 'PROCESSED BY NOC') {
                            i.NotificationApp.send("Proses Ticket " + msg2.ticket_reference + "",
                                "Name : " + msg2.nama + "</p>Action : " + msg2.deskripsi +
                                "</p>By NOC : " + msg2.nama_exekutor + "</p> ", "top-right", "#1ea69a",
                                "info")
                        } else if (msg2.status == 'FORWARD TO TECHNICIAN') {
                            i.NotificationApp.send("Forward Ticket " + msg2.ticket_reference + "", "" + msg2
                                .nama + "</p>Action : " + msg2.deskripsi + "</p>By NOC : " + msg2
                                .nama_exekutor + "</p> ", "top-right", "#1ea69a", "info")
                        } else if (msg2.status == 'PROCESSED BY TECHNICIAN') {
                            i.NotificationApp.send("Proses Ticket " + msg2.ticket_reference + "", "" + msg2
                                .nama + "</p>Action : " + msg2.deskripsi + "</p>By TN: " + msg2
                                .nama_exekutor + "</p> ", "top-right", "#1ea69a", "info")
                        } else if (msg2.status == 'CLOSED BY NOC') {
                            i.NotificationApp.send("Hold Ticket " + msg2.ticket_reference + "", "" + msg2
                                .nama + "</p>Action : " + msg2.deskripsi + "</p>By NOC: " + msg2
                                .nama_exekutor + "</p> ", "top-right", "#da8609", "warning")


                        } else if (msg2.status == 'CLOSED BY TECHNICIAN') {


                            i.NotificationApp.send("Hold Ticket " + msg2.ticket_reference + "", "" + msg2
                                .nama + "</p>Action : " + msg2.deskripsi + "</p>By TN: " + msg2
                                .nama_exekutor + "</p> ", "top-right", "#da8609", "warning")


                        } else if (msg2.status == 'CLOSED BY CS') {


                            i.NotificationApp.send("Closed Ticket " + msg2.ticket_reference + "", "" + msg2
                                .nama + "</p>Action : " + msg2.deskripsi + "</p>By CS: " + msg2
                                .nama_exekutor + "</p> ", "top-right", "#5ba035", "success")


                        }


                    }
                    console.log('ticket non', msg2);

                }(window.jQuery);
            });

                order: [
                    [4, "asc"]
                ],

                }
